Ads and I have been stuck in the office most of this week trying to finish off our latest project...I’m sure most of you can agree that being stuck at a desk for hours can make you feel FLAT 🤯😑
Fun fact for you (which Adam actually told me 😜) after 90minutes working on a task, your brain power starts to decrease and it becomes harder to work (and think) at your full potential! 🧠
SO
Make sure you guys have a reset every 90min! Even if you can’t go for a walk, get up, have a stretch, a bathroom break, fill up your drink bottle, walk around the office...anything to get your mind off the task your doing so you can come back at 100% 👊🏼 #lunchbreak #brainpower

How long should I hold a stretch? 🤔 If you’re wanting to improve flexibility, holding your stretches for at least 1 minute is a good target 🎯
Our muscles have a natural stretch reflex (which stops sudden excessive stretching & protects us from injury) SO, if you are purposely stretching to gain flexibility you should aim to gently stretch through this reflex...
Flexibility is all about time under tension, it takes around 20secs to ease through the stretch reflex & then all the gains happen after that! 💪🏼😁 If you focus on taking big breaths it also makes it wayyyy less painful & easier to get deeper 😌
BONUS...here’s my personal secret to really improving my flexibility: Stretch everything twice over! Along with stretching a little bit every day (usually after my workouts), 1-2 times a week I’ll do a deep stretch session and double stretch things like splits, back bends, and trouble spots like my hip flexors and glutes 😉 The second time round allows your body to get deeper into your stretch & also build better muscle memory for future flexibility! 🤗 #flexibilitytraining #stretching

Sometimes it can feel like you can’t give everyone what they want. Including yourself.

Stop.
Breathe.
Remember that you can only do the best you can do.
And that is enough.
Be kind to yourself,
Keep fighting.
You will get back on top.
I promise.
One step at a time.

Been missing from insta for a little while 😉 but I’ve purposefully taken some special time with my family here in Poland 🇵🇱♥️
